  "texts": [
    "Redundancy of data is another critical issue on point clouds.",
    "Point cloud representations can be highly redundant, compared to meshes representations, especially on planar surfaces.",
    "The latter results in large files that cannot be shared or stored.",
    "In such cases, the point cloud needs to be efficiently organized to provide good representations that could be feasibly processed.",
    "Finally, the last basic challenge in point cloud processing is the existence of noise in the resulting models."
  ],
